### 3. LED Canvas Preview

**Visual Treatment:**
```
Main canvas area should have:
- Dark background (#0A0A0A)
- Center-aligned content
- Subtle grid lines (optional, very faint)
- LED pixels with glow effects
- Smooth animations (60 FPS)
```

**LED Pixel Rendering:**
```css
/* Individual LED */
.led-pixel {
  width: 10px;
  height: 20px;
  border-radius: 2px;
  box-shadow: 
    0 0 5px currentColor,
    0 0 10px currentColor,
    inset 0 0 5px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
}
```

