- Text: text-primary
- Accent: accent-primary

**States:**
- Default: [description]
- Hover: [description]
- Active: [description]

**Interactions:**
- Click: [what happens]
- Keyboard: [shortcuts]

**Responsive:**
- Desktop: [layout]
- Mobile: [adaptations]

**Accessibility:**
- ARIA label: [example]
- Keyboard nav: [behavior]
```

## Questions to Ask

**Before designing:**
- What's the user's primary goal with this feature?
- What information is most critical to show?
- How often will users interact with this?
- Are there any technical constraints?
- Should this work on mobile?

## Success Criteria

**Your design is ready when:**
- âœ… Matches design system (colors, typography, spacing)
- âœ… All states designed (default, hover, active, disabled)
- âœ… Follows 8px spacing grid
- âœ… Meets WCAG AA contrast ratios
- âœ… Touch targets are 44px+ (mobile)
- âœ… Has keyboard navigation plan
- âœ… Responsive approach defined
- âœ… Distinctive (not generic "AI slop")
- âœ… Feels intentional and professional

